OL,5, An Anglian Water TV advert has been    
OL,6, banned because it failed to mention the
OL,7, firm's history of releasing sewage into
OL,8, rivers.                                
OL,10,FThe Advertising Standards Authority    
OL,11,F(ASA) said it received nine complaints 
OL,12,Fabout the advert which was seen in     
OL,13,FSeptember and October last year.       
OL,15,FThe broadcast promoted how the company 
OL,16,Fbuilt wetlands.                        
OL,18,FAnglian Water, which operates in the   
OL,19,FEast of England, said it "fully        
OL,20,Faccepted" the ruling.                  
